{
  "texts": [
    "A review of universities adopting generative models and how those models evolved, highlighting their current rapid and revolutionary development is presented.",
    "Research on generative models' optimal use and Egypt readiness is examined to develop a roadmap for Egyptian Universities use of generative models.",
    "LITERATURE REVIEW A.",
    "Universities Adopting Generative ModelsEgypt did not make generative models like ChatGPT officially accessible until November 2023 even though ChatGPT was officially introduced to the public in November 2022 [1].",
    "As a result, Egyptian universities are lagging in the use of generative models."
  ]
}